title: Amazon FBA Best Seller Rank (BSR)  Explained
description:
Keepa is a chrome extension. Just go to your Chrome browser, Settings, Extensions and search for keepa.  It will appear and download it. Now when you open an Amazon page the Keepa chart will populate below each product page you open.


Sign up for Amazon FBA
